# Optional: PageIndex reads LiteLLM keys from `pageindex/.env` when you run
# Python inside that folder. You do NOT need this file if you already set
# VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY in the project root `.env` — `npm run pageindex:run-example`
# maps it to GEMINI_API_KEY for you.

# GEMINI_API_KEY=your_google_ai_studio_key
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_ai_studio_key
